---
title  : Pitstop
summary: Life-cycle build tool
contact: Trans <transfire@gmail.com>

description:
  Pitstop is an advanced life-cycle build system.
  With Pitstop, build tasks are user defined service
  instances tied to stops along a track. Whenever the
  pistop console command is run, a track is followed
  from beginning to designated destination.

requires:
  - redtools
  - facets
  - pom
  - qed (test)

resources:
  home: http://rubyworks.github.com/pitstop
  code: http://github.com/rubyworks/pitstop
  mail: http://groups.google.com/rubyworks-mailinglist

repositories:
  public: http://github.com/proutils/pitstop.git

authors:
  - Thomas Sawyer

